paragraphs.title: Defino universo de mal configurados desde la tabla de casuisticas (tablero integral)
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_01;
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_01 stored as orc as 
select 
*
from sandbox.jg_tablero_terminales a
where
a.mes=date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM') -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------CAMBIAR periodo
--and a.tipo_cliente_de in('Individuo','Empresa')
and a.unidad_negocio='Movil'
and a.fl_navegador='NAVEGADOR'
and a.fl_total_so not in('actualizable', 'Obsoleto')
and a.fl_terminal in ('Mala configuracion')
;

paragraphs.title: Idem parrafo anterior (2022 05 06)
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

/*Este parrafo replica el anterior pero reemplazando el filtro fl_terminal por unos analogos utilizando la fuente de AT_tac y los IMSIS del trafico*/
drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_imsis_trafico_01;
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_imsis_trafico_01 stored as orc as

select * from (select ani, imsi, fecha, row_number() over (partition by ani order by fecha desc) as orden from trafico.comptel_xdr_consolidado a
where fecha between date_format(date_sub(current_date,day(current_date)),'yyyyMM01') and date_format(date_sub(current_date,day(current_date)),'yyyyMMdd') ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------->Fecha
group by ani, imsi, fecha)x where x.orden=1;


drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_01;
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_01 stored as orc as 

select 
a.*
from sandbox.jg_tablero_terminales a
left join access_data.at_tacs_gsma_m b on a.tac_nr=b.tac_nr and b.periodo_nr=a.mes
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_imsis_trafico_01 c on a.ani=substring(c.ani,3,10)
left join ANALYTICS.off_xdr_mes_5_out_modoff d on a.ani=substring(d.ani,3,10)  and d.aniomes=a.mes
where
a.mes= date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM') -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------CAMBIAR periodo
--and a.tipo_cliente_de in('Individuo','Empresa')
and a.unidad_negocio='Movil'
and a.fl_navegador='NAVEGADOR'
and a.fl_total_so not in('actualizable', 'Obsoleto')
--and a.fl_terminal in ('Mala configuracion')
and b.banda_general_tx ='LTE Compatible'
and substring(c.imsi,8,1) = '9'
and d.mb_4g = 0
;

paragraphs.title: Veo vive-trabaja-mayor
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc (hive)

drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_02;
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_02 stored as orc as 
select 
a.*,
case when a.cei_ind_experiencia_total_nr<70 then 1 else 0 end as fl_cei_70,
case when a.cei_ind_experiencia_total_nr<60 then 1 else 0 end as fl_cei_60,
case when a.mb_tot>=500 then 1 else 0 end fl_500_mb,
case when a.mb_tot>=1000 then 1 else 0 end fl_1_gb,
b.base_cell_id as celda_mayor,
b.dias_con_trafico_ca dias_trafico_mayor
from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_01 a
join elementos_red.indicador_cei_mensual_prevalencia b on a.ani=b.valor_recurso_primario_cd and a.mes=b.fecha_foto_id
;

drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_03;
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_03 stored as orc as 
select 
a.*,
c.base_cell_id as celda_trabaja,
c.dias_con_trafico_ca dias_trafico_trabaja
from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_02 a
join elementos_red.indicador_cei_mensual_trabaja c on a.ani=c.valor_recurso_primario_cd and a.mes=c.fecha_foto_id
;

drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_04;
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_04 stored as orc as 
select 
a.*,
d.base_cell_id as celda_vive,
d.dias_con_trafico_ca dias_trafico_vive
from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_03 a
join elementos_red.indicador_cei_mensual_vive d on a.ani=d.valor_recurso_primario_cd and a.mes=d.fecha_foto_id;

paragraphs.title: Tecno de cada Sitio
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_05;
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_05 stored as orc as 
select
c.*
from
(select
b.*,
row_number () over(partition by mes, id_celda order by fl_estado, fecha_de_estado desc) rnk
from
(select
a.*,
case when estado = 'Comercial' then 1
     when estado = 'PruebasLTE' then 2
     when estado = 'Swap' then 3
     when estado = 'Integrado' then 4
     when estado = 'Liberado' then 5
     when estado = "Planificado" then 6
     when estado = 'Des-definido' then 7
     when estado = 'Baja' then 8
     else 9
     end fl_estado
from
(select
substring(fecha, 1,6) as mes,
id_celda,
sector,
estado,
sitio,
latitud,
longitud,
radio_de_cobertura,
altura,
azimuth,
apertura_horizontal,
banda_mhz,
tipo_inst_sitio,
localidad,
provincia,
cabecera,
region,
subregion,
tecnologia,
fecha_de_estado
from tableros.listado_celdas_sectores
where fecha = date_format(date_sub(current_date,day(current_date)),'yyyyMMdd') ----------------------------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>> ultimo dia mes 
and id_celda is not null) a) b) c
where rnk = 1;


drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_06;
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_06 stored as orc as 
select
mes,
sitio,
sum (case when tecnologia='2G' then 1 else 0 end) fl_2G,
sum (case when tecnologia='3G' then 1 else 0 end) fl_3G,
sum (case when tecnologia='4G' then 1 else 0 end) fl_4G,
sum (case when tecnologia='NULO' then 1 else 0 end) fl_nulo
from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_05
group by mes,sitio
;

drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_07;
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_07 stored as orc as
select
a.mes,
a.sitio,
(case when a.sitio = 'indefinido' then '8. indefinido'
when fl_2g>0 and fl_3g>0 and Fl_4g>0 then '1.Todos'
when fl_2g=0 and fl_3g>0 and Fl_4G>0 then '2.3G y 4G'
when fl_2g=0 and fl_3g=0 and Fl_4G>0 then '4.Solo 4G'
when fl_2g>0 and fl_3g=0 and Fl_4G=0 then '7.Solo 2G'
when fl_2g=0 and fl_3g>0 and Fl_4G=0 then '6.Solo 3G'
when fl_2g>0 and fl_3g=0 and Fl_4G>0 then '3.2G y 4G'
when fl_2g>0 and fl_3g>0 and Fl_4G=0 then '5.2G y 3G'
else 'ver' end) fl_sitio,
case when (b.sitio is null and d.sitio is null) then 0 else 1 end as fl_sitio_banda_4,
case when c.sitio is null then 0 else 1 end as fl_sitio_banda_2,
case when e.sitio is null then 0 else 1 end as fl_sitio_banda_7,
case when f.sitio is null then 0 else 1 end as fl_sitio_banda_28,
case when g.sitio is null then 0 else 1 end as fl_sitio_banda_5,
case when h.sitio is null then 0 else 1 end as fl_sitio_banda_2_5
from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_06 a
left join (select mes, sitio, count(sitio) as Q from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_05 where banda_mhz ='1700/2100' group by mes,sitio)b  on a.sitio=b.sitio and a.mes=b.mes
left join (select mes, sitio, count(sitio) as Q from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_05 where banda_mhz ='1900' group by mes,sitio)c  on a.sitio=c.sitio and a.mes=c.mes
left join (select mes, sitio, count(sitio) as Q from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_05 where banda_mhz ='2100' group by mes,sitio)d  on a.sitio=d.sitio and a.mes=d.mes
left join (select mes, sitio, count(sitio) as Q from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_05 where banda_mhz ='2600' group by mes,sitio)e  on a.sitio=e.sitio and a.mes=e.mes
left join (select mes, sitio, count(sitio) as Q from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_05 where banda_mhz ='700' group by mes,sitio)f  on a.sitio=f.sitio and a.mes=f.mes
left join (select mes, sitio, count(sitio) as Q from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_05 where banda_mhz ='850' group by mes,sitio)g  on a.sitio=g.sitio and a.mes=g.mes
left join (select mes, sitio, count(sitio) as Q from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_05 where banda_mhz ='850/1900' group by mes,sitio)h  on a.sitio=h.sitio and a.mes=h.mes
;

paragraphs.title: Le pego la tecno de cada sitio por ani
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc (hive)
drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_08;
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_08 stored as orc as
select 
a.*,
d.sitio as sitio_mayor_vf,
c.sitio as sitio_trabaja_vf,
b.sitio as sitio_vive_vf
from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_04 a
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_05 b on b.id_celda=a.celda_vive
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_05 c on c.id_celda=a.celda_trabaja
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_05 d on d.id_celda=a.celda_mayor
;

drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_09;
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_09 stored as orc as
select 
a.*,
b.fl_sitio as fl_sitio_mayor_vf,
c.fl_sitio as fl_sitio_vive_vf,
d.fl_sitio as fl_sitio_trabaja_vf
from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_08 a
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_07 b on b.sitio=a.sitio_mayor_vf
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_07 c on c.sitio=a.sitio_trabaja_vf
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_terminales_mal_config_07 d on d.sitio=a.sitio_vive_vf
;
